{"tid":40111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支國國債價格跌停😏","createTime":"2016-12-15T03:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T05:27:38.000Z","uid":58309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ea496c15f00d56fe9957ce9d36134246bf8ae2","tid":40111,"uid":58309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"共產黨係咪已經被（老破）破產😏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHK ToolBar\t本地兩岸                              <br />\n內地國債期貨價格跌停<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=912468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D912468&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8pkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=bd29874d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=912468</a><br />\n<br />\n中國債市近期已持續受壓，加上美國聯儲局加息四分一厘，而且點陣圖暗示明年或加息三次，多於之前的預測，導致今早中國國債期貨暴跌，五年和十年期國債期貨價格跌停，十年期國債跌百分之二觸及跌停板，是上市以來最大跌幅。在內地債災拖累下，中資金融股受壓，工商銀行(<a href=\"http://01398.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01398.HK&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8pkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=2ddef9f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01398.HK</a>)、建設銀行(<a href=\"http://00939.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00939.HK&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8pkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=d5e1463f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00939.HK</a>)和中國銀行(<a href=\"http://03988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03988.HK&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8pkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=1967314b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03988.HK</a>)，跌百分之二，工行報4.58元，建行報5.58元，國壽(<a href=\"http://02628.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02628.HK&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8pkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8fa77de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02628.HK</a>)跌百分之三，報20.8元。"},{"pid":"22025c7e58e339d5d49fe0713786e5da1fba5c4c","tid":40111,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"個yield係咁升"},{"pid":"0dd1c9f9f26a1e2d7a615b12e44c709dbf910aac","tid":40111,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"個個沽貨轉倉？"},{"pid":"6d3e6b5179fd6afd6381dce7174ce44502385c21","tid":40111,"uid":28934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀芽</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c5258faffa14de25d5c07fa0991a62acf059e6","tid":40111,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"四分一已經咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1847407fc520f9c031669d5af2d784bf647310e2","tid":40111,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"個emoji用得好"},{"pid":"2b24ae0e5af7c071ef003909e7d9e36307143054","tid":40111,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:27:38.000Z","msg":"支爆近了，好友應當悔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}